{"tid":632074,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"有人收我阿爺間樓 但有咁嘅條款","createTime":"2018-04-17T05:16:58.000Z","updateTime":"2018-04-17T08:45:43.000Z","uid":42655,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"9ae1307e92a4b77f6f7c60a7416ce5f9d2122e1a","tid":632074,"uid":42655,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-17T05:16:58.000Z","msg":"我阿爺住係舊樓 有代理黎收樓(重建) 價就唔係特別好 屋企人話考慮下 但係見到有咁嘅條款<br />\n<br />\n佢份約就話必買必賣 即係簽作之無得反悔 反口就要賠錢 咁正常樓宇買賣都有㗎啦 <br />\n<br />\n但係佢多樣野 就係話如果佢收唔夠某個百分比就可以唔賣 唔駛賠錢<br />\n<br />\n ching有冇類似經驗? 比d意見比小弟<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/05.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ede2551b2cac30959eb25ea5e1b9a8cdcd9be3e8","tid":632074,"uid":44454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-17T05:18:15.000Z","msg":"搵律師啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1736257897eb1ce96eca0d9f983761e0b5bfaaff","tid":632074,"uid":129878,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-17T05:20:10.000Z","msg":"佢成世收唔齊, 你層樓咪冇得賣?係咪有個限期??"},{"pid":"b4bef392935d46a380a239fb123b7eed82411d26","tid":632074,"uid":42655,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-17T05:26:00.000Z","msg":"分析下雙方講論點<br />\n<br />\n我方:<br />\n簽左約就半年內冇得反口 有人出更高價都唔賣得 白白比佢鎖住但最後都可能賣唔出 又冇錢賠<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/02.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n佢一句收唔夠 我根本唔知真定假 變左佢想反口就反口<br />\n<br />\n買方 <br />\n保障翻自己公司 做唔成都唔會蝕<br />\n好多人都係咁(佢話)"},{"pid":"6060c7d020b54867a65f6ebd3a5fb673203678b3","tid":632074,"uid":42655,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"1736257897eb1ce96eca0d9f983761e0b5bfaaff","tid":632074,"uid":129878,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-17T05:20:10.000Z","msg":"佢成世收唔齊, 你層樓咪冇得賣?係咪有個限期??"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-17T05:26:14.000Z","msg":"半年"},{"pid":"e3a470f9798250a4bd8c6a49b9f319d99705c7ef","tid":632074,"uid":130365,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-17T05:43:15.000Z","msg":"咁佢出咩offer 可唔可以講下"},{"pid":"21be4dce5096b99df57044d28cc496223e0dc607","tid":632074,"uid":164938,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-17T06:37:51.000Z","msg":"咁你本身有無諗住賣先"},{"pid":"f26867148e0790d4a4624404ad8e014408be941b","tid":632074,"uid":44171,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-17T06:57:30.000Z","msg":"呢個係法例規定, 要有一定比例同意先可以收購, 佢無點你.<br />\n<br />\n但早幾年將個例改左, 個比例降低左好多, 所以田生果D收樓先易左, 自己GOOGLE下法例先"},{"pid":"d3813518583a6b1587f26043638d0a8d21e331b7","tid":632074,"uid":9231,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-17T07:02:04.000Z","msg":"收邊棟？土瓜灣？<br />\n幾錢呎？<br />\n同埋你條款唔滿意可以同佢傾"},{"pid":"e1de89f427b046728eecd2372467baff601eafee","tid":632074,"uid":42655,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"f26867148e0790d4a4624404ad8e014408be941b","tid":632074,"uid":44171,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-17T06:57:30.000Z","msg":"呢個係法例規定, 要有一定比例同意先可以收購, 佢無點你.<br />\n<br />\n但早幾年將個例改左, 個比例降低左好多, 所以田生果D收樓先易左, 自己GOOGLE下法例先"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-17T07:53:09.000Z","msg":"呢個我知 法例係過某百分比可以強拍<br />\n<br />\n問題係收唔夠咁點?<br />\n我白白簽死半年比佢 佢駛唔駛賠番訂金<br />\n正常買樓都係要沒收訂金<br />\n佢宜家就係唔比訂金<br />\n所以就覺得有問題"},{"pid":"64b82a74d61869a1e5fb735b3ee3b3edf17063de","tid":632074,"uid":110832,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-17T07:55:03.000Z","msg":"搵律師問啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"365e71c5d16c08f9b931eac5e0e44290ff89d3db","tid":632074,"uid":42655,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"d3813518583a6b1587f26043638d0a8d21e331b7","tid":632074,"uid":9231,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-17T07:02:04.000Z","msg":"收邊棟？土瓜灣？<br />\n幾錢呎？<br />\n同埋你條款唔滿意可以同佢傾"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-17T07:55:43.000Z","msg":"中西區 <br />\n同佢傾佢就話無事個個都係咁<br />\n又成日暗(明)示好多人簽左 <br />\n兇9我咁款<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c9d70bbd86924f4a145e58c30d3e78becf616953","tid":63207